-- Socgen Sees `Risk' of Verbal Intervention on Koruna by Czech Central Bank
-- Chris Kirkham
-- 2010-07-29T06:52:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/socgen-sees-risk-of-verbal-intervention-on-koruna-by-czech-central-bank.html

          
          
             Societe Generale says there’s an
“elevated” risk Czech central bankers will verbally intervene
to control the koruna before policy makers meet next week. The
analysts said they’re “surprised” central bankers have been
“quiet” so far.  
